Jangan lakukan itu.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:04.200
Jika kau begitu mengkhawatirkanku,

00:13:04.600 --> 00:13:06.040
mengapa kamu membawa gadis itu kembali?

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:07.440
Jika kau begitu mengkhawatirkanku,

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:10.600
mengapa kamu lebih peduli tentang
kebahagiaannya daripada kebahagiaanku?

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:12.560
Bu, tolong...
- Lihat.

00:13:13.800 --> 00:13:15.120
Jangan datang padaku.

00:13:15.880 --> 00:13:16.920
Pergi.

00:13:17.560 --> 00:13:18.560
Pergi kesana.

00:13:19.520 --> 00:13:20.720
Pergi ke dia.

00:13:21.040 --> 00:13:22.280
Aku bukan siapa-siapa.

